column5: Well Its 8 hours till the guys and I are off to Nakina then straight north by Luenenbergers to our cottage in the middle of nowhere. Will post a big report, here is crossing my fingers to good weather....it's snowing there right now!
Wish you guys best of luck weather wise and enjoy yourselves Tight lines Leechman
Have a great time.  I'm sure you'll be up around the Albany watershed and the fishing will be amazing.  Here's hoping for some warmer weather in the north for ya.
